overview.en: BBQ achieves the transfer of ownership through block chain technology, so that developers and consumers can create and exchange assets through the platform, from assets to records to ownership, and create rights and interests passport.
overview.zh: BBQ通过区块链技术来实现所有权等的转移，让开发商和消费者也能够通过该平台创建和交换资产，从资产到记录再到所有权等，打造权益通证。
